        "heading": "<h2>Qure mobile app</h2>",
        "text": "<p><strong>The only FDA-cleared LED light therapy mask with an app.</strong></p><p>Your skin is unique, so your treatment should be too.</p><p>Choose between <em>three treatment modes</em>, “Skin Rejuvenating”, “Skin Clearing” or custom treatment zones. Select a treatment mode on five different facial areas to <em>treat and target what your skin needs today. </em></p><p>Never miss a treatment with Qure mobile app planner and phone reminders.</p>",
